<metal:block i18n:domain="schooltool">
  <div class="header" i18n:translate="">
    What is This?
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <p i18n:translate="">
      SchoolTool's database file should be periodically "packed" to reduce its filesize.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
      Packing removes old transactions from the database.  It can take
      a long time on a large database, so packing should be done in
      off-peak times.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
      Before packing, a backup file will be saved as Data.fs.old
    </p>
  </div>
</metal:block>
